comments: The practice of advance techniques for land cover analysis.

Learning how to do a project from zero. I spent a lot of time on thinking the project and tried to finding possible solution to the question. This is a very valuable experience. The professor also provide some experience when actually doing real project and I think this is very useful.
Opportunity to build on skills of introductory remote sensing class; extensive readings of journal articles prepares students for conducting their own publishable research.

comments: She was always available to answer questions and help with the labs.
Although Qingling is not TA for this class, he is wonderfully helpful and responsive.
Professor was available. Class could benefit from having a TA.

narratives.question_text: Discuss if you wish how this course fits into your overall program.
comments: Interested in doing remote sensing research, and this class was very helpful for developing skills to do high-quality research.

narratives.question_text: Why did you take this course?
comments: Because I'm interested in applying Remote Sensing techniques to decision making processes that involve information from different approaches.

narratives.question_text: Did it live up to your expectations?
comments: I learned a lot from this course and it is beyond my expectations.
